5-(methylsulfanylmethyl)piperidin-3-ol has the following elements and their respective number of atoms:
- Carbon (C) x 12
- Hydrogen (H) x 19
- Nitrogen (N) x 1
- Oxygen (O) x 1
- Sulfur (S) x 1

Adding up the total number of atoms: 
12 (C) + 19 (H) + 1 (N) + 1 (O) + 1 (S) = 34 atoms

Therefore, there are 34 atoms in 5-(methylsulfanylmethyl)piperidin-3-ol.
